Country Justice Pilot Episode
The Fayette County Sheriff's K-9 unit will be featured in a new pilot called "Country Justice" set to air at 10 p.m. Tuesday on Animal Planet. A production team followed the deputies and their canine partners around for two weeks over the summer.
The film crew sent their footage to Animal Planet for a pilot. If the pilot does well Tuesday, the film crew will return to Fayetteville to film another 30 weeks for a full season.
